      <title>欧洲央行将再次降息，并暗示经济增长放缓将进一步放松政策</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecb-cut-rates-again-signal-further-easing-growth-falters-2024-12-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧元区通胀已接近目标且经济陷入衰退，欧洲央行几乎肯定会在周四再次降息，并暗示2025年将进一步放松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecb-cut-rates-again-signal-further-easing-growth-falters-2024-12-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 23:06:27 GMT</pubDate>
