      <title>消息人士称，美国银行提拔 387 名员工为董事总经理</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-america-promotes-387-employees-managing-director-source-says-2024-12-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士周三告诉路透社，美国银行已在 2024 年将 387 名员工提拔为董事总经理，比去年增加 16%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-america-promotes-387-employees-managing-director-source-says-2024-12-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 20:42:54 GMT</pubDate>
